[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1]It's the second day of summer school...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_001_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14802 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]I know it's hot, everyone, but let's just try and get through class. Focus pocus! Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Still, who would've thought people would actually attend this course over the summer? You sure are a curious lot.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]I'm not really sure what to make of that...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Well, anyway, let's talk about something interesting today.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 1 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]All you future magicians will want to pay close attention... Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_002_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Today's subject is tarot. That's right, those cards often used in fortune telling.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Despite originating in 15th-century Europe as normal playing cards, tarot cards evolved into tools of divination.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]There are a variety of tarot card decks, including the Marseille and the Rider decks...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]But today, in honor of the great Crowley, we will be using the Thoth deck.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_003_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14806 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]First, let's talk about the composition of the deck...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The modern 78-card tarot deck is divided into two parts.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]There are 22 Major Arcana—the face cards—and 56 Minor Arcana, or number cards...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Minor Arcana are also sometimes called pip cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Major Arcana feature a variety of illustrations on their faces.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Beginning with the Fool and ending with the Universe...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]They tell a story in numerical order that represents an individual's journey through life.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Each Major Arcana represents a stage on that journey...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]And each stage represents an event an individual must experience to achieve wholeness.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_004_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14807 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]They are all important, so let's take a look at each of the 22 cards, one by one.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The first card, numbered 0, is the Fool. It represents beginnings and suggests infinite possibilities.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]In other words, the beginning of life.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_005_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The next card, the Magician, represents action and initiative... but also immaturity.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The High Priestess represents contemplation and inner knowledge.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Empress represents both motherhood and maternal love as well as one's vitality.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Emperor is an opposing card. It represents fatherhood as well as leadership and decision-making skills.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Hierophant represents formality and knowledge. It is a symbol for religion.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_006_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14805 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Lovers represent choice. Here, the individual finally begins to develop a conscience.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Chariot represents the individual's victory, but only a momentary one.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Justice is exactly what it sounds like: knowing what is right and what is wrong.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Hermit represents self-reflection. In other words, searching for answers deep within one's heart.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Fortune represents fate, and the opportunities it brings.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Strength represents both passion and self-control. It is depicted as power with reason.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The Hanged Man reflects the individual's inability to take action.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Spiritual death awaits the individual with the thirteenth card, which is aptly named Death.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Death is considered a transitional card...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]With death, the old ends, and the new begins.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_007_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14808 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Now, let us move on to what happens following the transition.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Temperance is the balancing of opposites. Opening one's eyes to the world allows for growth...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]And then an encounter with the Devil is where one faces temptation...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]At the Tower, the individual's values will start to collapse. It seems as if there's nothing to believe in...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The individual then finds a glimmer of hope in the Star, granting one peace and serenity.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]In turn, this makes one vulnerable to the Moon's illusions, which gives way to fear and trepidation.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]But the individual may be rewarded with a bright future by the Sun, which signifies true achievement.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_008_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Judgement awaits the individual at the journey's end when looking back on the path one has traveled.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The final card is the Universe, which represents the individual reaching full awareness.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_009_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]And that's the growth of an individual as explained by the tarot cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 1 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Perhaps all this talk about life doesn't hit home with you young folks just yet, hm? Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_010_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14804 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Well, now you can use all 78 cards to divine the future in detail...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]...But most people only use the 22 Major Arcana.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Okay. Next, let's talk about fortune telling using the Major Arcana.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]First, you will need to shuffle the cards.[n][uf 1 1][e]
