[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 1 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]How are you all handling the heat? I could brew you some of my special tea if you'd like... Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_014_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Now, let's continue with our special summer course, The Truth Behind Magic.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]I'll be talking about Kabbalah.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]I assume all of you have at least heard of Kabbalah, yes?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]It is known as the mystical study of the Hebrew scriptures, but...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]As I've mentioned before, it had a great impact on Western sorcery.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]It has been said that, to learn the secrets of magic, you must first understand Kabbalah.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_015_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14815 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]So, who was the person who formed this incredible ideology known as Kabbalah?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Well, according to legend, it was Moses.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Yes, that Moses. The Moses who gave us the Ten Commandments and split the Red Sea.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_016_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]But in reality, it was formulated by a group of rabbis long, long ago.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]However, because it features such a complicated coded system...[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_017_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Kabbalah did not become known to the Western world until much later.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Now, it is important to note that there are many different ancient methods of deciphering Kabbalah.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]For example, there is Gematria, the interpretation of text by replacing letters with the numbers they represent.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]There is Notarikon, where you take a letter from each word to form another sentence or thought.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]There is also Temurah, a method where letters of words are replaced, thereby giving the sentence a new meaning.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]All these different methods make it difficult to fully comprehend Kabbalah.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_018_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14806 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Now, one of the most important ideas of Kabbalah is the Tree of Life, comprised of the ten Sefirot.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Most illustrations depict it as a chart shaped like a tree.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]The ten nodes represented by the Sefirot and the 22 paths connecting them...[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]All come together to form a map of God's creation and the spiritual ascent of man.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Where did we come from? Where are we going? These answers lie in the Sefirot.[n][uf 1 1][e]

[msg MSG_019_0_0 [Mr. Edogawa]]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]When training your magic, it's important to picture the Sefirot every so often.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]And when you are meditating, you should focus on the Sefirot as well.[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]This is going to be on the test, you know. They say knowledge is another form of magic, so study hard![n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 1 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]If you find yourself struggling, well, you may wish to turn to the Sefirot... Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]

