[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 0 65535 65535 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]By the way, did you all notice that I said there were 22 paths?[n][uf 1 1][e]
[uf 0 5 65278][uf 2 1][uf 4 5 1081 1 65535 65535 0 0][uf 3 1 3 0 65535 14823 0 0][uf 5 21 0 1081]Yes, that's right. The same number as the Major Arcana I spoke of before... Eeeheehee...[n][uf 1 1][e]
